34
00:03:06.019 --> 00:03:07.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（主人）いらっしゃいませ

35
00:03:08.688 --> 00:03:11.065 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（京極）
おお ウワサをすれば海原はん

36
00:03:11.649 --> 00:03:13.026 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
