38
00:03:18.156 --> 00:03:19.657 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（中川(なかがわ)得夫）ああ 士郎さん

39
00:03:20.783 --> 00:03:22.660 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
フン うっとうしいやつめ

40
00:03:22.994 --> 00:03:24.412 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
