しゃしゃり出てきおって

41
00:03:24.537 --> 00:03:25.413 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
なに？

42
00:03:25.997 --> 00:03:29.417 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
まあまあまあ
今日のところは わしの顔に免じて

43
00:03:29.626 --> 00:03:30.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ひとつ穏便に

44
00:03:43.473 --> 00:03:46.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（京極）いやあ 海原はんが
この店のことを書かれてるんで

45
00:03:46.643 --> 00:03:48.394 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
