46
00:03:49.145 --> 00:03:52.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
フグは関西が本場と
言われていたのは昔のこと

47
00:03:53.233 --> 00:03:56.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
