いやあ これはおおきに

52
00:04:16.631 --> 00:04:17.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いらっしゃいまし

53
00:04:18.341 --> 00:04:19.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（正木(まさき)）あの…

54
00:04:19.467 --> 00:04:21.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（正木の妻）
予約をお願いした正木ですが

55
00:04:22.095 --> 00:04:24.847 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（主人）はい 承っております
どうぞこちらに

56
00:04:25.014 --> 00:04:26.474 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ どうもすいません

57
00:04:28.601 --> 00:04:30.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ！ 失礼ですが

58
00:04:30.895 --> 00:04:33.356 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
海原雄山先生ではありませんか？

59
00:04:33.523 --> 00:04:34.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
そうだが

60
00:04:35.400 --> 00:04:37.944 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まあ 何て光栄なんでしょう

61
00:04:38.861 --> 00:04:41.572 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
先生のことは 以前から
尊敬申し上げております

62
00:04:41.948 --> 00:04:43.449 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
今日 この店に来ましたのも

63
00:04:43.783 --> 00:04:46.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
先生が褒めておられるのを
読んだからなんです

64
00:04:47.078 --> 00:04:49.497 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
さあさ
私どもも始めますんで

65
00:04:49.622 --> 00:04:53.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
