00:05:02.885 --> 00:05:05.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
最高においしいって
ここに書いてあるんで

71
00:05:05.346 --> 00:05:06.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
それを

72
00:05:06.431 --> 00:05:09.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
