それを食べに来たんです

73
00:05:10.059 --> 00:05:13.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ああ これは困りましたな

74
00:05:13.396 --> 00:05:15.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
実は今日は白子がないんですよ

75
00:05:15.773 --> 00:05:17.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
え？ そんなあ！

76
00:05:17.608 --> 00:05:19.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
白子がないんですか？

77
00:05:19.652 --> 00:05:24.866 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
