お取りにならんといけまへんな

102
00:06:45.655 --> 00:06:47.323 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
うん？ 私が？

103
00:06:47.448 --> 00:06:48.491 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（京極）そうや

104
00:06:48.616 --> 00:06:52.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
