食べられんでは殺生や

107
00:07:00.753 --> 00:07:01.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
いや しかし…

108
00:07:02.713 --> 00:07:05.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
