124
00:07:41.210 --> 00:07:42.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
わあ 光栄ですわ

125
00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.839 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
