126
00:07:45.256 --> 00:07:48.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
山岡はんが先にごちそうすると
言わはったんやから―

127
00:07:48.551 --> 00:07:50.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
山岡はんにも させてあげんと

128
00:07:51.804 --> 00:07:53.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あんたら幸せでんなあ

129
00:07:53.890 --> 00:07:57.935 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
