山岡さん これが例のものです

140
00:08:41.521 --> 00:08:42.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）わあ

141
00:08:42.980 --> 00:08:44.607 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（山岡）
こりゃ見事なタラだな

142
00:08:44.732 --> 00:08:47.276 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（職員）
ええ そりゃ最高ですよ

143
00:08:47.860 --> 00:08:49.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
これなら富山まで来た
かいがあったよ

144
00:08:49.904 --> 00:08:50.821 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（栗田）え？

145
00:08:50.947 --> 00:08:51.781 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
こいつをもらおうか

146
00:08:51.906 --> 00:08:52.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
（職員）あいよっ

147
00:08:55.952 --> 00:08:58.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（栗田）
山岡さん タラなんか買って―

148
00:08:58.454 --> 00:08:59.997 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
一体 何をする気なのかしら

149
00:09:03.417 --> 00:09:05.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
（栗田）
そして その日の夜

150
00:09:10.633 --> 00:09:14.011 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
海原雄山が指定してきた場所は
何と美食倶楽部(くらぶ)

151
00:09:14.887 --> 00:09:16.889 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
まさに海原雄山の城です

152
00:09:19.183 --> 00:09:21.060 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
何だか怖いわ

153
00:09:25.356 --> 00:09:28.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
山岡さん… ここが山岡さんの

154
00:09:29.986 --> 00:09:33.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:74.00% 
（山岡）
あの正木夫妻のためじゃなきゃ
こんな家に帰ってきはしないさ

155
00:09:34.115 --> 00:09:34.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あ…

156
00:09:41.831 --> 00:09:42.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
あっ

157
00:09:47.878 --> 00:09:49.797 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
